《'''最後一次'''》（{{lang-en|''The Last Time''}}）是美国創作歌手[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]的一首歌曲，收录于她的第4张录音室专辑《[[红_(泰勒·斯威夫特专辑)|红]]》。歌曲与[[雪警|雪警]]成员{{tsl|en|Gary Lightbody|加里·萊特波迪}}合作，是专辑的第7张也是最后一张单曲。两名歌手和歌曲的制作人{{tsl|en|Jacknife Lee|傑克耐夫·李}}共同创作了本歌曲。《最後一次》是一首受到[[民谣摇滚|民谣摇滚]]风格影响的[[另类摇滚|另类摇滚]]歌曲。<ref name=inquirer>{{cite web|last=Atilano|first=Joseph R.|title=Album Review: "RED" by Taylor Swift|url=http://entertainment.inquirer.net/67266/red-by-taylor-swift|work={{tsl|en|The Philippine Inquirer||The Philippine Inquirer}}|date=2012-11-13|accessdate=2013-10-20|archive-date=2017-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171224102857/http://entertainment.inquirer.net/67266/red-by-taylor-swift|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年10月19日，歌曲被送往[[BBC廣播二台|BBC廣播二台]]播放，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio2/playlist |title=BBC – Radio 2 – Playlist |work=[[BBC廣播二台|BBC Radio 2]] |publisher=[[英国广播公司|BBC]] |accessdate=2013-10-20 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131020082929/http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio2/playlist |archivedate=2013-10-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>11月4日，歌曲在[[當代流行電台|當代流行電台]]正式播出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/this-weeks-new-releases-04-11-2013-2586/ |title=This week's new releases 04-11-2013 |publisher=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]] |date=2013-11-04 |accessdate=2014-07-01 |author=Lane, Daniel |archive-date=2014-03-25 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140325125231/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/this-weeks-new-releases-04-11-2013-2586/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==音乐录像带==
歌曲的音乐录像带的導演為[[泰瑞·李察遜|泰瑞·李察遜]]，<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hitfix.com/news/taylor-swift-and-snow-patrols-gary-lightbody-in-the-last-time-video-watch | title=Taylor Swift and Snow Patrol's Gary Lightbody in 'The Last Time' video | last=Newman | first=Melinda | date=2013-11-18 | publisher=[[HitFix|HitFix]] | accessdate=2013-12-19 | archive-date=2013-12-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219151655/http://www.hitfix.com/news/taylor-swift-and-snow-patrols-gary-lightbody-in-the-last-time-video-watch | dead-url=no }}</ref>于2013年11月15日在[[Vevo|Vevo]]和[[YouTube|YouTube]]首播。录像带时长3分48秒，与专辑同名单曲《[[红_(歌曲)|红]]》相似，展现了泰勒絲和萊特波迪2013年8月27日在[[红巡回演唱会|红巡回演唱会]][[沙加緬度_(加利福尼亞州)|沙加緬度]]场次的表演镜头，这也是两人第一次同台演出。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://thethirdbarcom.wordpress.com/2013/08/28/capitalfm-taylor-swift-joined-by-snow-patrols-gary-lightbody-during-sacramento-tour-show/|title=CapitalFM: Taylor Swift Joined By Snow Patrol’s Gary Lightbody During Sacramento Tour Show|date=2013-08-28|publisher=|accessdate=2017-03-09|archive-date=2017-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904113356/https://thethirdbarcom.wordpress.com/2013/08/28/capitalfm-taylor-swift-joined-by-snow-patrols-gary-lightbody-during-sacramento-tour-show/|dead-url=no}}</ref>录像带以萊特波迪升至舞台开场，泰勒絲从其背后靠近，之后两人开始背对着坐下演唱。整个视频中可以看到粉丝自制的标语和他们的喝彩声。

